Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「众星」蕾佳 晶体转换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份仇恨 深刻体会到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是最后了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德战斗服解除 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洸 你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你呢 玲子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能晶体转换了  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 交给我了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洸 在这种时候 你干什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我触摸你和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以恢复你们的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是害羞的时候 快点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了 千晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下 玲子 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 洸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家的面前 太不成体统了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 太害羞了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 请互相爱抚 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 那种事居然能让能量上升!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 连我也开始变得奇怪了 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗从现在才开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神兽!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这个家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾佳空间 掩护!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来了 
